enhancement is the energetic driving force for phosphorylation-mediated 
regulation of OmpR-DNA binding. These findings suggest that OmpR 
phosphorylation-mediated activation follows the same paradigm as the other 
members of the OmpR/PhoB family of RRs in contrast to previously proposed models 
