Carbon Monoxide Gas Is Not Inert, but Global, in Its Consequences for Bacterial 
Gene Expression, Iron Acquisition, and Antibiotic Resistance.

Wareham LK(1), Begg R(2), Jesse HE(1), Van Beilen JW(3), Ali S(1), Svistunenko 
D(4), McLean S(1), Hellingwerf KJ(3), Sanguinetti G(2), Poole RK(1).

