ammonia-lyase (PAL) and biphenyl synthase 1 (BIS1) genes. The substrate 
specificities and the expression profiles indicate that the three 4CL isoenzymes 
are not involved in benzoyl-CoA biosynthesis in S. aucuparia cell cultures. 
