The glutathione-glutaredoxin system in Rhodobacter capsulatus: part of a complex 
regulatory network controlling defense against oxidative stress.

Li K(1), Hein S, Zou W, Klug G.

Author information:
(1)Institut für Mikrobiologie und Molekularbiologie, Heinrich-Buff-Ring 26-32, 
