We have undertaken a systematic search for T cell epitopes within the sequence 
of the major merozoite surface antigen (GP190) of Plasmodium falciparum. 
Recombinant polypeptides expressed in E. coli were used to evaluate the 
reactivity of peripheral blood mononuclear cells (PBMC) from both inhabitants of 
