regulation, while serving to repress the expression of hmpA. Furthermore, Fur is 
required for the proper expression and activation of the antioxidant enzymes, 
FeSOD and MnSOD. Finally, this work identified twenty-six new targets of Fur 
regulation, and demonstrates that H-NS repressed genes are down-regulated in 
Δfur.

