was constructed, which expresses the coding element of the Vibrio harveyi 
antigen AgaV-DegQ. TFM harboring pJAQ can secret AgaV-DegQ into the 
extracellular milieu. Vaccination of Japanese flounder with live TFM/pJAQ 
