protein genes (yehE, 07045, 11735, 11255). To investigate whether these 17 genes 
co-regulate the biofilm, the 17 identified genes were deleted from APEC strain 
APEC81. The results showed that except for the 11735 and 11255 genes, the 
deletion of 15 genes significantly reduced the biofilm formation ability of 
APEC81 (P < 0.05). The result of rdar (red, dry and rough) colony morphology 
showed that curli fimbriae genes (csgD, csgA, csgF, and csgG) and other 
functional genes (fimC, glxK, yehE, 07045, and 11255) affected the colony 
