Sheikh A(1), Khanam F, Sayeed MA, Rahman T, Pacek M, Hu Y, Rollins A, Bhuiyan 
MS, Rollins S, Kalsy A, Arifuzzaman M, Leung DT, Sarracino DA, Krastins B, 
Charles RC, Larocque RC, Cravioto A, Calderwood SB, Brooks WA, Harris JB, Labaer 
J, Qadri F, Ryan ET.

Author information:
(1)International Centre for Diarrhoeal Disease Research, Bangladesh (ICDDR,B), 
