anaerobic fermentative and respiratory growth. The expression of both lctEP and 
alsSD is strongly induced under anaerobic conditions. Anaerobic lctEP and alsSD 
induction was found to be partially dependent on the gene encoding the redox 
regulator Fnr. The observed fnr dependence might be the result of Fnr-induced 
