PUTRalsRBACE-PUTRinfC-rplT) were identified as having the highest activity, with 
expression outputs of 170%, 137%, 409%, and 203% of that of the PBAD promoter, 
respectively. These engineered PUTRs are stable for the expression of different 
genes, such as the red fluorescence protein gene and the β-galactosidase gene. 
