regulator that activates locus of enterocyte effacement (LEE)-dependent 
adherence in enterohemorrhagic Escherichia coli (EHEC). LEE activation by GrvA 
requires the Rcs phosphorelay response regulator RcsB and is sensitive to 
physiologically relevant concentrations of bicarbonate, a known stimulant of 
