suf genes did not show up in the microarray analysis. Therefore, we used qRT-PCR 
analysis and found that cobalt induced the suf operon expression. Moreover, 
kinetic analysis of the cobalt-mediated induction of the suf operon expression 
allowed us to propose that cobalt toxicity is caused first by impaired Fe/S 
biogenesis, followed by decreased iron bioavailability and eventually oxidative 
stress.

