Dual molecular signals mediate the bacterial response to outer-membrane stress.

Lima S(1), Guo MS, Chaba R, Gross CA, Sauer RT.

Author information:
(1)Department of Biology, Massachusetts Institute of Technology, Cambridge, MA 
