E. coli hmp mutant in aerobic conditions; however, Cgb fails to protect an hmp 
norR mutant in the absence of oxygen. Reduction of Cgb and Ctb in E. coli and C. 
jejuni soluble extracts and turnover after NO oxidation is demonstrated. 
