self-transferable by conjugation to Escherichia coli J53, azide-resistant. The 
Tra1 and Tra2 conjugative transfer regions of the IncHI2 plasmid R478 were found 
by in silico search. p17277A_477 is a complex plasmid that provides a large 
baggage of both resistance genes and genetic resources for plasmid 
rearrangements and additional resistance gene acquisition.

