Jia Y(1), Lu H(2), Zhu L(3).

Author information:
(1)College of Environmental and Resource Sciences, Zhejiang University, Hangzhou 
310058, China; Zhejiang Provincial Key Laboratory of Organic Pollution Process 
and Control, Hangzhou 310058, China.
(2)College of Environmental and Resource Sciences, Zhejiang University, Hangzhou 
