resultant hybrid proteins were consistent with models predicting that UhpC and 
UhpT have identical transmembrane topologies, with 10 to 12 transmembrane 
segments, and that UhpB has 4 to 8 amino-terminal transmembrane segments that 
anchor the polar carboxyl-terminal half of the protein to the cytoplasmic side 
of the inner membrane.

