glucose-6-phosphate (G6P) was assessed by RT-qPCR. The genome of all clinical 
isolates was sequenced by MiSeq (Illumina). Two first-step mutants were obtained 
in vitro from CFT073 (MICs, 128 mg/L) with single mutations: G469R in uhpB (M3); 
