(MICs, 0.5-8 mg/L) were devoid of any mutation. At least one genetic change was 
detected in all but one fosfomycin-resistant clinical isolates (MICs, 32 - >256 
mg/L) including 8, 17, 18, 5, and 8 in uhpA, uhpB, uhpC, uhpT, and glpT genes, 
